data.description: ACTIVE WITH CONTRACT/ACCEPTING BACKUP OFFERS. PRICE IMPROVED! This is what Florida living is all about with combined indoor and outdoor living! Step through the Front Double Doors into the Private Courtyard and Pool Area. This Beautiful Home wraps around the 1586 sq ft Courtyard with Pool AND features a Cabana/Casita Suite, with Full Bath, which is separate from the main home. This floorplan is great for out-of-town guests, an in-law suite, or home office. The possibilities are endless!!. This 3 Bed/3 Bath home comes with freshly painted interior, newer stainless-steel kitchen appliances, custom UV Solar shades throughout and new baseboards and door trim. The Master Bedroom has custom woven wood shades and boasts a very large walk-in closet. The Spacious Master Bath features a garden tub, walk-in shower, dual sinks, granite countertops, and private water closet. This distinctive home offers 360 views of the private courtyard and pool from every room in the home AND a view of the 286 sq foot rear lanai overlooking the fenced backyard. Some upgrades include a 2020 ROOF, 2021 top of the line 18-Seer HVAC System with humidity control, air purification system with new duct work, along with pool equipment and new ductless mini-split HVAC system installed in the Cabana. Please see the attached List of Improvements as there are many more than are listed here. Several Interior Photos Are Virtually Staged. Pristine Place is a gated community with amenities such as clubhouse, fitness center, playground, community pool, and tennis court. The Suncoast Parkway is less than 2 miles away offering easy access to Tampa and Gulf Beaches.
